    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What is Large Language Model 
    &lt;div id=&#34;what-is-large-language-model&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
